OL,6,FPoliticians in are debating whether
OL,7,Fassisted dying should be legalised in
OL,8,Fthe island.
OL,10,FThe debate started on Tuesday 21 May
OL,11,Fand has entered its second day.
OL,13,FThe proposition to introduce was
OL,14,Flodged by the Council of Ministers on
OL,15,FMonday 25 March and argued that it
OL,16,Fshould be legalised as long as
OL,17,F"essential provisions and safeguards"
OL,18,Fare met.
OL,20,FPoliticians have been debating two
OL,21,Froutes of assisted dying:
