OL,6,FDeputy Andy Howell says: "I fear that
OL,7,Fon a prosperous island, there will
OL,8,Falways be tensions especially where
OL,9,Ffamilies have so much to gain in terms
OL,10,Fof property and inheritance.
OL,12,F"I urge you to also vote against
OL,13,F'Route 1', medics do get it wrong, we
OL,14,Fcannot afford to make mistakes, human
OL,15,Flife is to be treasured."
OL,17,FDeputy David Warr adds: "No matter
OL,18,Fwhich way I vote today, there will be
OL,19,Fa number of constituents who firmly
OL,20,Fbelieve that my decision was the wrong
OL,21,Fone.
