OL,4,Cvotes in assisted dying debate
OL,6,F"When aids was discovered amongst the
OL,7,FLGBTQ+ community there was real
OL,8,Fsocietal prejudice towards that
OL,9,Fcommunity. If assisted suicide had
OL,10,Fbeen available at that time, would
OL,11,Fthere have been such an urgency to
OL,12,Ffind appropriate drugs?
OL,14,F"Today those infected can now enjoy a
OL,15,Fquality of life which at the time
OL,16,Fnever seemed possible, an example that
OL,17,Fthe sanctity of life should always be
OL,18,Fgiven primacy.
